data.description: Wow, this home has a view unlike any other! Located on the beautiful Fairway Terrace North in the Colonial Park Subdivision be prepared for the breathtaking scenes in the backyard.  Natural park and pond in backyard with coy fish, varying types of ducks with the seasons, and plenty of towering trees surrounding. HOA cares for front and back yards beyond the wood fencing.  Wood burning fireplace in spacious living room with Tall Vaulted Ceilings, this is a no carpet home, with light colored flooring throughout. Did you say marble?  Yes, light marble counter tops in kitchen, and included in bathroom along with beautiful dark blue tile work.  Stainless Steel Appliances, plenty of pantry and cabinet space, kitchen looks into living room.  The bathrooms have updated bowl sinks, and fixtures, including oversized shower head. Views, Views, Views from Master Bedroom, closet lined with cedar. Fenced backyard with storage shed, and concrete slab space great for BBQing etc. New Roof 2023!
